<h2>5.3 Active Parking Tariffs</h2>
<ul type=disc>
  <li>Standard Car: 20,000 VND / hour</li>
  <li>SUV / Large Vehicle: 30,000 VND / hour</li>
  <li>Electric Vehicle (EV): 20,000 VND / hour (EV charging surcharge: 15,000 VND / hour)</li>
  <li>Motorbike: 5,000 VND / hour</li>
  <li>Handicap / Priority: 10,000 VND / hour</li>
</ul>

